Define the sample in bcgsfhs_sample.sex.  Use read_bcgsfhs_sample() to
read it.

* Sky-subtract and pre-process the mosaics:
  bcgsfhs_skysubtract

* Cut out and write just the BCG image and model:
  bcgsfhs_get_bcg, /debug

* Ellipse-fit the BCGs
  bcgsfhs_ellipse

* Fit Sersic models to the surface-brightness profiles
  bcgsfhs_sersicfit
